article.description: — Justin Johnson had 23 points and 10 rebounds for his third double-double this season and UT Rio Grande Valley defeated Lamar 67-63 on Wednesday.
article.headline: UT Rio Grande Valley defeats Lamar 67-63
article.linkText: UT Rio Grande Valley defeats Lamar 67-63
article.story: BEAUMONT, Texas -- — Justin Johnson had 23 points and 10 rebounds for his third double-double this season and UT Rio Grande Valley defeated Lamar 67-63 on Wednesday. Xavier Johnson scored 15 points for the Vaqueros (8-21, 3-14 Western Athletic Conference. Marek Nelson scored 12 points Brock McClure led the Cardinals (2-26, 0-17 WAC) with 12 points. Lincoln Smith scored 11 points as did C.J. Roberts. Jordyn Adams scored 10 points. ----
